<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html lang="ja" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<title>CSS Test: text-combine-upright, whitespace inside tcy with insufficient line space</title>
<link href="https://www.upsuper.org" rel="author" title="Xidorn Quan" />
<link href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-writing-modes-3/#text-combine-layout" rel="help" />
<link href="reference/text-combine-upright-break-inside-001-ref.xht" rel="match" />
<meta content="line should never be broken inside text-combine-upright text node" name="assert" />
<link href="support/tcy.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<style>
.test { writing-mode: vertical-rl; }
.test &gt; p { height: 3em; margin: 0 5em; }
.tcy, .fake-tcy { color: transparent; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<p>Test passes if the two columns are identical.</p>
<div class="test">
  <p>XXXXX<span class="tcy">X X</span>XXXXX</p>
  <p style="white-space: nowrap">XXXXX<span class="fake-tcy">X</span>XXXXX</p>
</div>


</body></html>